SUMMARY:Trivia @Brewsters
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\n🎉 Trivia Night Alert! 🧠✨\nI’
 m cross-posting this event with Marin Millennials\, 20s30s North Bay\, and
  Sonoma Marin Brat Pack—so the RSVP count here might not show the full c
 rowd. Expect a fun group!\nJoin us for Trivia Night hosted by North Bay Tr
 ivia! 🏆 Come test your knowledge\, win some prizes\, and enjoy great fo
 od and drinks while you’re at it.\nI’ll try to get there around 6:30 P
 M to snag a good table—feel free to come early and say hi!\n🌙 Heads u
 p: It’s an outdoor event\, so dress warm. I hear they’ve got heated la
 mps\, which should definitely help!\nBring your brainpower and your good v
 ibes—see you there! 🎯🍻
